259
00:12:29.958 --> 00:12:30.959
Capisce?

260
00:12:31.042 --> 00:12:32.043
Will. I forgot to tell you--

261
00:12:32.127 --> 00:12:33.503
Hey. kids. come on.
Get in the tub.

262
00:12:33.587 --> 00:12:34.754
Here we go. here we go.

263
00:12:41.928 --> 00:12:43.722
Whatever.

264
00:12:45.557 --> 00:12:46.558
<i>You need money?</i>

265
00:12:46.641 --> 00:12:47.642
<i>Well. you're in luck</i>

266
00:12:47.726 --> 00:12:50.312
<i>'cause you can start earning</i>
<i>up to 300 bucks per day.</i>

267
00:12:50.395 --> 00:12:54.774
