<i>on BigBroncoCrypto...</i>

268
00:12:55.275 --> 00:12:58.236
Frank.
I'm pregnant again.

269
00:12:58.320 --> 00:13:01.072
That's amazing. sweetheart.

270
00:13:01.156 --> 00:13:05.577
You know.
we needed another one of those.

271
00:13:05.660 --> 00:13:07.120
Hey. Will...

272
00:13:07.204 --> 00:13:09.122
...gonna need that rent money.

273
00:13:33.230 --> 00:13:34.314
Boom!

274
00:13:34.397 --> 00:13:36.024
Check these out.

275
00:13:36.107 --> 00:13:39.319
Vineland green. Fillmore Fours.
in the flesh.

276
00:13:39.402 --> 00:13:41.404
Jett wore these
in the Furball game.

277
00:13:41.488 --> 00:13:43.657
Normally.
these sell for around six...

278
00:13:43.740 --> 00:13:46.576
...but I'll give it to you

279
00:13:46.660 --> 00:13:47.661
for five.

280
00:13:47.744 --> 00:13:50.288
No. not the Fours.

281
00:13:50.372 --> 00:13:52.207
Oh. I wanted those.

282
00:13:52.290 --> 00:13:53.667
But you're broke.

283
00:13:53.750 --> 00:13:56.002
But if I had the Fours
I wouldn't look it.

284
00:13:56.086 --> 00:13:59.172
Ah. Yes. Yes. you would.
It's gonna be okay.

285
00:13:59.256 --> 00:14:02.133
Pristine upper mesh. Taut laces.

286
00:14:02.217 --> 00:14:03.843
Mmm.

287
00:14:03.927 --> 00:14:05.762
- Nutty.
- Nasty.

288
00:14:05.845 --> 00:14:06.763
250.

289
00:14:06.846 --> 00:14:08.848
- Come on.
- 250? How dare you.

290
00:14:08.932 --> 00:14:10.559
The disrespect.

291
00:14:10.642 --> 00:14:12.936
Come on. Will.
I can do installments.

292
00:14:13.019 --> 00:14:15.939
Yeah. yeah. that's great. Daryl.
but my landlord can't.

293
00:14:16.022 --> 00:14:17.899
Okay.

294
00:14:17.983 --> 00:14:19.901
I can't watch this.

295
00:14:19.985 --> 00:14:22.070
So. 400?

296
00:14:22.612 --> 00:14:24.030
- 240.
- I-It's going down?

297
00:14:24.114 --> 00:14:25.407
- 230.
- Dang. stop!

298
00:14:25.490 --> 00:14:26.616
Please. please!

299
00:14:26.700 --> 00:14:27.826
- Yo!
- No way!

300
00:14:27.909 --> 00:14:29.369
Y'all are not
gonna believe this.

301
00:14:29.452 --> 00:14:30.870
Mane is at the Cage.

302
00:14:30.954 --> 00:14:33.873
and he's taking on
all challengers.

303
00:14:35.750 --> 00:14:39.963
